OL,5, Serial killer Levi Bellfield is engaged
OL,6, and has applied to marry in prison, the
OL,7, Ministry of Justice has confirmed.     
OL,9,FA Downing Street spokesman said Boris  
OL,10,FJohnson was "sickened and appalled" by 
OL,11,Fthe murderer's request and his thoughts
OL,12,Fwere with the victims' families.       
OL,14,FBellfield, 53, will need the permission
OL,15,Fof the governor at HMP Frankland in    
OL,16,FCounty Durham.                         
OL,18,FHe is serving two whole-life sentences 
OL,19,Ffor the murders of Marsha McDonnell,   
OL,20,FAmelie Delagrange and Milly Dowler.    
